{"id": 1939, "genre": 1001, "title": "亲密关系中，你都犯过 or 见过哪些沟通上的错误？", "description": "好心办坏事，我也很无奈啊。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3638, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170930113034JjAnKNQgGHRcqI15.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-30T03:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 241923, "content": "叫他帮助我生病的女室友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806190}, {"id": 239112, "content": "把唠叨、抱怨当做坦诚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144512}, {"id": 240392, "content": "把什么事情都告诉对方，导致影响ta的情绪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148391}, {"id": 239113, "content": "以为关系好交谈不控制底线的怼骂，结果骂到绝交。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995104}, {"id": 239115, "content": "我给你的，何尝是你想要的，我却沾沾自喜，只感动了自己。事到如今，连对不起你都不愿听了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772313}, {"id": 239629, "content": "我原本以为……只有女孩需要陪伴，结果我自己也需要足够的陪伴和亲密接触……我们都是unique而平等的个体，所谓的“自私”也是正常的，只要在正常需求指标内都是正常的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019773}, {"id": 239885, "content": "说了太多，却没什么切题；讲得太少，表白得太突兀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117546}, {"id": 239887, "content": "记不住事 不喜欢也不说 憋着 真的内伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048778}, {"id": 240399, "content": "本想开个玩笑说，你是不是生病了，后来。。。她误会了，完了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147444}, {"id": 241935, "content": "冷暴力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155720}, {"id": 239888, "content": "最大的沟通错误就是不沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581967}, {"id": 240656, "content": "心❤里喜欢，就是不说出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 251924, "content": "总是否定我喜欢的事物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199177}, {"id": 239127, "content": "我用脑来提问，你用肺来回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144396}, {"id": 239128, "content": "在对方不给我发微信的情况下 我也赌气不给他回 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137166}, {"id": 239129, "content": "我以为你很懂我", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144525}, {"id": 239641, "content": "彼此", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729085}, {"id": 239897, "content": "“你就是一个烂好人呀”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112098}, {"id": 239386, "content": "以为很重要，", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038943}, {"id": 239131, "content": "逃避所有亲密关系，稍加亲近就觉得压力山大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140784}, {"id": 239132, "content": "买了个表开始吵架", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 239389, "content": "陷入一段无辜的爱情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948701}, {"id": 239134, "content": "自己以为很亲密。其实不是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143265}, {"id": 239902, "content": "过度关心伴侣像关心孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146741}, {"id": 239137, "content": "有毒的我养你", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017934}, {"id": 239393, "content": "用自己以为亲密的方式对待关系，结果发现对方并不觉得这是亲密，反而成为负担", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318209}, {"id": 239649, "content": "过度解读", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844738}, {"id": 239138, "content": "你不说我不说各自憋着", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555077}, {"id": 239394, "content": "男闺蜜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055758}, {"id": 243234, "content": "明明知道有些话不能讲，讲了就天涯陌路还是会讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134375}, {"id": 239139, "content": "相处很长时间的两个人，都以为对方会懂你，其实都不懂！", "image": "img/option/option/20170930145447IvER4MzYGk9xr7WB.jpg", "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144573}, {"id": 239140, "content": "到了最后千言万语想要挽留，可是说出口的却是一句冷冷的我们分手吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131457}, {"id": 239141, "content": "删好友，以及，冷漠。好傻。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888868}, {"id": 239397, "content": "误解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139688}, {"id": 240421, "content": "开始跟所有人都聊的很嗨，回去就跟路人一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702285}, {"id": 239142, "content": "空欢喜最令人难过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701087}, {"id": 239143, "content": "为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293255}, {"id": 239399, "content": "我以为…我以为…我以为…", "image": "img/option/option/20171001145517AMyF9Y7frjKlsp8t.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145132}, {"id": 240935, "content": "男人〈有的)女人为了爱都弯成呆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151302}, {"id": 239144, "content": "你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144593}, {"id": 240424, "content": "好像不应该强求 彼此对于生活各种细节的认同，可总觉得求同存异 很难做到……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98794}, {"id": 239145, "content": "很多东西不愿解释，总觉得清者自清，但别人不这么想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144595}, {"id": 239401, "content": "我是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068247}, {"id": 239658, "content": "很难接受女朋友比之前了解到更加复杂的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124233}, {"id": 240682, "content": "以为从前的顺从都是ta的喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119194}, {"id": 239147, "content": "不要说闺蜜男朋友的坏话，即便他们分手了。因为他们一旦复合…你就成了坏人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542691}, {"id": 239919, "content": "不沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592243}, {"id": 239152, "content": "在超市储物箱边，突然一个不是我的箱门打开了，顺手把他关上了。其实是另一边别人扫码打开拿东西，没拿就被我关上了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025993}, {"id": 239153, "content": "异国恋，我想着可能由于时差和节奏上的差别，各自忙的时间也不同，但是一跟她视讯就说自己忙忙忙，到现在我已经抵触跟她沟通……其实谁不懂要多沟通的道理呢？但是如果那一方把房门紧闭，再敲下去，终究也会累的吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094106}, {"id": 239154, "content": "过度揣摩", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684875}]}